title: DDFP 233: Packers Randall Cobb, Daniel Jeremiah
itunes:title: DDFP 233: Packers Randall Cobb, Daniel Jeremiah
description:
Shek, Rank & Handsome Hank welcome wide receiver Randall Cobb into Studio 66 to discuss the state of the Green Bay Packers; catching the division-winning TD pass against the Bears; ranking today's QBs and his Mt. Rushmore of current cornerbacks; and more. Daniel Jeremiah also checks in from the road to project who'll shine at the 2014 NFL Scouting Combine and what it'll take for the Browns to make a quick turnaround in 2014. Plus, producer Black Tie's "Shout Outs" makes a return. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
